Assigns a filename to a specific group of messages. 
@returns boolean True is returned when the filename is writable and correctly bound to a group of messages. 
<code> assignGroup( (SUCCESS_AUDIT | FAILED_AUDIT), array(), array("Login/Logout"), "Security" ) assignGroup( (ERROR | FATAL), array(), array(), "error") assignGroup( DEBUG, array("Paynet"), array(), "paynet_debug");
</code>

